<h>Britons fail to battle the bulge as 26 per cent of men AND women classed as obese</p>

<p>By Claire Bates</p>
<p>Last updated at 4:09 PM on 15th December 2011</p>
<p> The number of overweight and obese men and women and obese-only men and women has gradually increased since 1993</p>
<p> Obesity can cause a number of health problems including type 2 diabetes and heart disease</p>
<p> Men aged 55 to 64 were the most likely to be overweight or obese (82%)</p>
